HAHA!!!!

Jag bara bläddrade in här, kollade lite på kommentarerna utan att direkt läsa, men "såg" "Ursäkta?"

Så jag fick kolla vad som stod där.. xD ja, jag kommer inte sluta skratta på en lång tid iallafall..

sound quality is HORRIBLE. it's like he placed a mic near a speaker. you can hear chatter in the background and there's also other music that cuts in out of the blue. it's like someone changed the channel.  I wanted the usher brandy track and sounds horrible. 

save your time and don't bother downloading.
